snippet.title: DIRT 5 | Energy Content Pack and Free Update | Out Now! | Xbox, PlayStation, PC
snippet.description:
🎮 DIRT 5 - OUT NOW on Xbox, PlayStation, Steam, Windows Store and Google Stadia! https://dirtgame.com/dirt5 

DIRT 5's Energy Content Pack and FREE Update 3.00 are rolling out now for all platforms!

ENERGY CONTENT PACK
⚡ Four new cars 
⚡ 25 new Career events
⚡ New sponsors
⚡ New liveries 
⚡ New customisation options 

FREE UPDATE 3.00
⚡ Junkyard Playgrounds Update
⚡ New Playgrounds location: Italy
⚡ New iconic liveries
⚡ Technical improvements

The Energy Content Pack is FREE to all Amplified Edition or Year One Upgrade players! Available on digital stores for other players 🖐️ 
 
Patch notes | https://bit.ly/3534rmB

🔴 Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/dirtgame?sub_confirmation=1 

👾 Discord: https://discord.com/invite/BYGnqQB 

🐤 Twitter: https://twitter.com/DiRTGame 

📘 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dirtgame 

📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dirtgame/ 

👽 Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/dirtgame
